 "name": "RPlog_Mourning",
 "title": "Mourning",
 "summary": "In the sleepless aftermath of a catastrophe, the Jedi Jessalyn Valios huddles alone in a hotel room, staring at the carved staff of her fallen enemy and consumed by guilt over the events that sent Orson, Han Solo, and Luke to the hospital. In parallel introspection, the brooding mechanic Orson wrestles with the fear and anger creeping in after glimpsing the Dark Side so vividly, and the dark adept Simon Sezirok looms over the reflections of all involved. The log is a quiet, multi-perspective meditation on grief, guilt, and the seductive pull of darkness in the wake of a costly confrontation.",
